that you're watching here.

03:22.911 --> 03:26.121
And I want you to listen
to my broadcast on Friday

03:26.206 --> 03:28.332
and come to church
on Sunday.

03:28.416 --> 03:30.042
I'll tell you
all about it.

03:34.923 --> 03:38.342
Welcome back.
This is KYGL,
Oldies on the Border.

03:38.426 --> 03:40.469
It's Halloween night,
so if you're sitting
at home,

03:40.553 --> 03:42.638
waiting for the
trick-or-treaters
to come by,

03:42.722 --> 03:44.640
we'll keep you company with
our usual bag of tricks.

03:44.724 --> 03:47.517
Real people died,
you know, young man.

03:47.602 --> 03:49.353
Real people died.

03:49.437 --> 03:50.979
That's right.
That's right.

03:51.064 --> 03:53.857
It's a godless film
and I want to see you
on Sunday.

03:53.942 --> 03:55.442
We welcome you.

03:58.238 --> 04:00.781
That's good. You leave.
This is a godless film.

04:00.865 --> 04:03.075
It's good that
you're leavin'.

04:34.565 --> 04:35.649
What?

04:38.486 --> 04:40.654
I'm just having
a good time
with you, Jami.

05:10.101 --> 05:13.520
The only reason I play
football is to get a
scholarship and go to SMU.

05:13.855 --> 05:15.605
Yeah?

05:15.690 --> 05:17.316
And how about you?
Where'd you apply?

05:18.860 --> 05:20.777
