You did apply, right?

05:20.862 --> 05:22.279
You're, like,
super smart.

05:22.363 --> 05:25.115
Yeah.
Yeah, I did.

05:25.199 --> 05:27.951
I applied
to UT Austin,

05:28.036 --> 05:29.536
NYU,

05:30.204 --> 05:31.621
