05:31.706 --> 05:32.956
Wow.

05:33.041 --> 05:34.458
That's impressive.

05:34.542 --> 05:37.210
Oh, I probably won't get in,
but, you know, aim high.

05:37.295 --> 05:38.670
You should.

05:43.217 --> 05:45.469
My dad used to write
for the Gazette, actually.

05:45.553 --> 05:47.763
My grandma says
it's in my blood, so...

05:47.847 --> 05:48.805
Even though no one reads it,

05:48.890 --> 05:50.390
I like writing for the paper.

05:50.475 --> 05:51.475
I could do that from here

05:51.559 --> 05:53.393
and stay close to my grandma.

05:53.478 --> 05:54.811
If I don't get in.

05:54.896 --> 05:56.063
Right.

06:01.402 --> 06:03.236
Well, I'm glad
you finally said yes.

06:04.405 --> 06:05.697
Me, too.

